              "expose": [],
              "Layout": {}
            },
            "markup": "\u003Ch2\u003EGet in Touch\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Cp\u003EFeel free to contact the Office of the CIO Service Desk if you would like to learn more about the Office of the CIO and the services that we provide. The \u003Ca target=\u0022\u0022 data-router-slot=\u0022disabled\u0022 href=\u0022https://serviceportal.ne.gov/KnowledgeBase/View/152#!/\u0022 data-anchor=\u0022#!/\u0022 title=\u0022serviceportal.ne.gov\u0022 type=\u0022external\u0022\u003EService Portal located here\u003C/a\u003E is available to all @nebraska.gov teammates who can create and track requests. \u0022Don\u0027t have an @nebraska.gov account?\u0022 You can speak to us directly by calling \u003Ca target=\u0022\u0022 data-router-slot=\u0022disabled\u0022 href=\u0022tel:402-471-4636\u0022 title=\u0022\u0022 type=\u0022external\u0022\u003E402.471.4636\u003C/a\u003E or \u003Ca target=\u0022\u0022 data-router-slot=\u0022disabled\u0022 href=\u0022tel:800-982-2468\u0022 title=\u0022\u0022 type=\u0022external\u0022\u003E800.981.2468\u003C/a\u003E and one of our coordinators will be happy to assist you in submitting your request.\u003C/p\u003E"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "63f94cfe-9040-40d2-bdb6-e7722f56b89b",
      "key": "2e08997b-83b2-4c51-b93e-de31cd61d10c",
